        h2.rework-title#google-pixel-2-xl
          | Google Pixel 2 XL
          a.ml-2(href="#google-pixel-2-xl") #
        h3.text-assistive Pure CSS Google Pixel 2 XL, Google Pixel 2 XL in pure CSS
        .rework-content
